Java program to convert Celsius to Fahrenheit:

firstly, I have created a class TemperatureCeltoFor.
method to convert celsius to fahrenheit
I have defined the main method to begin the execution
I have declared the variables celcius and fahrenheit with double datatype.
I have created a Scanner class to take input from the user.
I am assking user to enter the celcius value.
I am storing the value into the variable celsius.
I am converting the celcius into the fahrenheit
I am displaying the result.
 
Testcase:

Conversion from Celsius to Fahrenheit and from Fahrenheit to Celsius has an important role in the conversion of units system. In this post, we will develop a Java program to convert Celsius to Fahrenheit.

The formula used to convert from Celsius to Fahrenheit is given as, ⁰F= (⁰C * 9/5) + 32

Input-1:

Enter the celcius value

 26
 
Output-1:
 
Fahrenheit value = 78.80

Input-2:

Enter the celcius value

 45
 
Output-2:
 
Fahrenheit value = 113.00
